				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				To twist songs you can do a number of things.<BR>
You can set up a song macro like<BR>
<BR>
/stopsong<BR>
/cast 1<BR>
/pause 30, cast 2<BR>
/pause 30, cast 3<BR>
/stopsong<BR>
<BR>
Or you can twist the gems.<BR>
Try going to the board &quot;Class Specific&quot; and clicking on the bard box for LOTS of relevant information regarding twists, and other bard info.<BR>
Regards,<BR>
Gileas Dreamsinger, MM server, bard of the 33rd string
